import { Box, Grid, Container, Typography } from '@material-ui/core';
import Page from '../components/Page';
import {
  AppTeachers,
  AppStaff,
  AppKelas,
  AppNewsUpdate,
  AppStudents,
  AppOrderTimeline,
  AppCurrentVisits,
  AppWebsiteVisits,
  AppTrafficBySite
} from '../components/_dashboard/app';

const waveStyle = 'span'(({ theme }) => ({
  [theme.breakpoints.up('sm')]: {
    top: -7,
    zIndex: 1,
    width: 12,
    right: 20,
    height: 12,
    arialabel: 'arrow'
  }
}));

export default function DashboardApp() {
  return (
    <Page title="Home | Linguo ID">
      <Container maxWidth="xl">
        <Box sx={{ pb: 5 }}>
          <Typography variant="h4">
            Hello, Abdil
            <waveStyle role="img" className="wave">
              ðŸ‘‹
            </waveStyle>
            (Students)
          </Typography>
        </Box>
        <Grid container spacing={3}>
          <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={3}>
            <AppStudents />
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={3}>
            <AppTeachers />
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={3}>
            <AppKelas />
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={3}>
            <AppStaff />
          </Grid>

          <Grid item xs={12} md={6} lg={8}>
            <AppWebsiteVisits />
          </Grid>

          <Grid item xs={12} md={6} lg={4}>
            <AppCurrentVisits />
          </Grid>

          <Grid item xs={12} md={6} lg={8}>
            <AppNewsUpdate />
          </Grid>

          <Grid item xs={12} md={6} lg={4}>
            <AppOrderTimeline />
          </Grid>

          <Grid item xs={12} md={6} lg={4}>
            <AppTrafficBySite />
          </Grid>
        </Grid>
      </Container>
    </Page>
  );
}
